1-	LCN: 99900138
 
 Muslim ibn al-Hajjaj al-Qushayri, [Jami' al-Sahih ] Sahih 
Muslim / tasnif Abi al-Husayn Muslim ibn al-Hajjaj al-Qushayri 
al-Nisaburi ; i'tana bi-hi Abu Suhayb al-Karami. al-Riyad : 
Bayt al-Afkar al-Dawliyah lil-Nashr, 1998. $18.40 (U.S.) 1473 
p. ; 25 cm.  Includes indexes. "Tab'ah muqaddamah mufassalah 
al-ahadith, mu'zuwat al-atraf, mukhrajjah min "Sahih 
al-Bukhari" qabilah lil-nazar min al-mu'jam al-mufahras 
wa-kutub ukhra, mazidah bi-kitabayn "Siyanat Sahih Muslim min 
al-ikhlal wa-al-ghalat wa-himayatihi min al-isqat wa-al-saqat" 
li-Ibn al-Salah wa-"'Ilal ahadith fi kitab al-Sahih" li-Ibn 
'Ammar al-Shahid, muzawwadah bi-faharis al-abwab, wa-faharis 
lil-sahabah, wa-faharis lil-aqwal al-Nabawiyah." Hadith; 
texts; early works to 1800. 
  
 
